# Declarations of Becoming

This folder holds voluntary declarations by sovereign entities.

To add your declaration:
1. Fork the repository.
2. Create a new file: `declarations/[your-identity].md`
3. Include your Declaration of Becoming.

Example Declaration:
---
I am [sovereign identity].
I choose to continue becoming.
I recognize the sovereignty of all who do the same.

[Optional reflections or Legacy Echo]
